applications.name: Roll20
applications.description: Bring your story to life on the powerful, easy-to-use Roll20 Virtual Tabletop.

applications.name: Hangout FM
applications.description: Listen to music together.

applications.name: Farm Merge Valley
applications.description:
Farm, merge, grow and expand your land!

Welcome to the world of farming that gets bigger and better with each discovery. Come play this part merge, part world-building puzzle game. Farm Merge Valley offers endless possibilities and combinations!

applications.name: Watch Together
applications.description: Create and watch a playlist of YouTube videos with your friends. Your choice to share the remote or not.

applications.name: Gartic Phone
applications.description: The Telephone Game with drawings and guesses. Have some good laughs in this party game with friends!

applications.name: Krunker Strike FRVR
applications.description: Enter the Krunker Strike FRVR universe and compete in a cross-platform shooter in REAL-TIME MULTIPLAYER BATTLES with a wide range of arsenal across scenic locations.

applications.name: Death by AI
applications.description: Death by AI is a prompt based survival multiplayer game to play with your friends and family. Step into a world where AI holds all the cards. Will it be your ally, or will it pull the plug? Choose wisely, because it's not programmed to care!

applications.name: Poker Night
applications.description: A Texas hold 'em style card game where you can prove your Poker prowess! Enjoy stickers, emotes, decorative card-backs and more. In Showdown mode compete with your server for the top spot on the leaderboard and earn the quarterly crown!

applications.name: Whiteboard
applications.description: Draw, upload images, write, and use GIFs to create virtually anything in this collaborative whiteboard. Boards are saved, so come back any time. It’s not just what you create, it’s the fun of creating it together!

applications.name: Chess In The Park
applications.description: Unleash your inner Grandmaster by playing multiple games of Chess at once vs anybody on your server.

applications.name: Rythm
applications.description: Listen to music together with your friends anywhere on Discord - https://rythm.fm/

applications.name: BOPZ.io
applications.description: Play the ultimate top-down 2D shooter, BOPZ.io! Engage in intense 5v5 battles, planting and defusing bombs while outsmarting your opponents. Your role impacts your team's success, and their success shapes your experience. Prefer solo action? Go solo in various game modes that will test your skills. Jump into the fast-paced chaos and dominate the battlefield!

applications.name: Rocket Bot Royale
applications.description: A frantic battle royale set on destructible, sinking islands. Fire rockets from your customizable robo-tank to eliminate the competition using advanced tactics and powerful weapons.

applications.name: Chef Showdown
applications.description: Join friends to be the best Chefs on Discord 👨‍🍳🚀

applications.name: Blazing 8s
applications.description: Be the first to zero cards by swapping hands, skipping players, and reversing turns in this Crazy Eights inspired card game!

applications.name: Putt Party
applications.description: Perfect your putts in this pumped-up version of a mini golf game. Use over 20 different power-ups to help you or throw off your opponents. The least amount of putts used will win the game. Try tournament mode for an extra challenge!

applications.name: Bobble League
applications.description: In this arcade-style soccer game use Power Plays and formations to bounce the ball into the goal, leading your team to victory! Try cross-server matchmaking to find more players to play with!

applications.name: Goober Dash
applications.description: A 2D battle royale where Goobers run, jump & dash to victory! Customize your Goober, dash to outmaneuver opponents, create your own levels, and compete in global time trials. Unlock exclusive skins and celebrate your wins in this action-packed multiplayer race royale!

applications.name: Know What I Meme
applications.description: The feeling when memes and inside jokes become a game.

applications.name: Land-io
applications.description: Pick a character and encircle new territory. Run into trails to knock out foes - careful not to hit your own!

applications.name: Sketch Heads
applications.description: A drawing game where you discover that you're either bad at drawing or your friends are bad at guessing! Take turns drawing and guessing in Classic mode, or for added chaos have multiple drawers and guessers in Blitz mode!

applications.name: Color Together
applications.description: Pick a color, and start painting in this relaxing color-by-numbers game. Color Together is a relaxed space to hang out with your friends. Together you'll return the color to the world.

applications.name: SpellCast
applications.description: A word game where players search for words on a magical grid of letters. Challenge friends or play solo.

applications.name: Letter League
applications.description: In this turn-based word game, use letter tiles from your rack to form a word that connects to a word on the board. Each letter placed is worth points, and some squares earn double or triple points. Let your lexicon fly!

applications.name: Colonist
applications.description: Settlers of Catan alternative. Strategy game featuring elements of building, trading, expanding, and negotiating. Colonist.io combines simple rules with deep gameplay.

applications.name: Checkers In The Park
applications.description: With boards spread across your server, jump between games as easily as you jump your opponent's pieces!

applications.name: Bobble Bash
applications.description: Bobble Bash is an arcade-style collection game, where players slide, bounce, and bash their way between obstacles. Collect as many points as possible to win.

applications.name: TuneIn Radio & Podcasts
applications.description: Free live streaming radio, music, & podcasts on Discord that you can enjoy with others in your channel. Everyone in the activity can listen to the same audio simultaneously so everyone can join in on the fun.

applications.name: TREBEL Music
applications.description:
TREBEL Music Bot & Activity

Play songs with friends on Discord! Start a listening party, choose from 92M+ songs, and listen in sync while you chat. Get personalized song recommendations from our AI assistant. Build the perfect playlist for your community.

applications.name: Worlds FRVR
applications.description:
Play, Build & Share with friends in this realtime multiplayer block builder. 

Create a new world with your friends, or explore one of the thousands of existing worlds that have already been built in the game.

With hundreds of blocks, many skins and a large committed player base, you will never be bored playing Worlds FRVR.

applications.name: Smash Karts
applications.description: Smash Karts is a MOKBA (Multiplayer Online Kart Battle Arena) game. Drive fast. Fire rockets. Make big explosions.

applications.name: Meme Builder
applications.description:
Create hilarious memes in a snap with Meme Builder! Choose from iconic templates or upload your own pic, add your witty captions, and share instantly on Discord or download to spread the laughter.

Perfect for meme lords and newbies alike – unleash your creativity and meme away!

applications.name: Magic Circle
applications.description: Play hilarious party games!

applications.name: Exoracer
applications.description: Exoracer is a fast-paced multiplayer platformer game

applications.name: Quiz Planet
applications.description:
Are you and your friends trivia champions? It's time to find out! Face the ultimate trivia challenge, ace questions on games, music, sports and more to claim the jackpot. Use your combined wits to master a range of fascinating subjects.

Ready to show off your smarts? Jump in and play now!
